  m_Name: artifactprovip
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::LocalizableString
  english: A sacred artifact holding ancestral memories. The Bronze Drum is sturdy
    but cannot fight back against the darkness. Use your skills to stop the monsters
    and protect the Drum at all costs!
  vietnamese: "N\u01A1i h\u1ED9i t\u1EE5 k\xFD \u1EE9c c\u1EE7a t\u1ED5 ti\xEAn,
    mang l\u1EA1i b\xECnh y\xEAn cho d\xE2n l\xE0ng. Tr\u1ED1ng \u0110\u1ED3ng r\u1EA5t
    ki\xEAn c\u1ED1 nh\u01B0ng kh\xF4ng th\u1EC3 t\u1EF1 v\u1EC7 tr\u01B0\u1EDBc
    s\u1EE9c m\u1EA1nh h\u1EAFc \xE1m. H\xE3y d\xF9ng m\u1ECDi k\u1EF9 n\u0103ng
    c\u1EE7a b\u1EA1n \u0111\u1EC3 ng\u0103n qu\xE1i v\u1EADt ti\u1EBFp c\u1EADn
    v\xE0 b\u1EA3o v\u1EC7 Tr\u1ED1ng b\u1EB1ng m\u1ECDi gi\xE1!"
